-- Rust TUI 7-layer pyramid (TestBackend, insta, PTY, viewport, accessibility, Gemini)
-- Gleam 8-category gold standard (C1-C8 with weights)
-- 100-cycle regression, long-duration monitoring, 4-phase split-screen runner
